title: Multistrike
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A weapon with this special rule grants its wielder a +1 to its Attacks characteristic during the Assault phase. This special rule stacks with itself, but only once, so the maximum number of additional attacks the wielder may make from this special rule is two, +1 each for wielding two weapons with this special rule.